                "name": "Magic Horn",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "While on the creature\u2019s head, an almiraj\u2019s horn is treated as a <i>+1</i> weapon. Any living creature slain by an almiraj\u2019s gore attack immediately turns to stone (as if by the <i>flesh to stone</i> spell, with no saving throw, and the creature is still dead). A severed almiraj horn retains a wisp of its former magic, and counts as a masterwork weapon if used to create a magical dagger or similar small piercing weapon."
